{"id":6596,"date":"2024-01-12T14:50:07","date_gmt":"2020-03-12T09:20:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=6596"},"modified":"2023-12-15T14:33:12","modified_gmt":"2023-12-15T09:03:12","slug":"home-bar-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-bar-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Set The Bar High With These Top Home Bar Designs And Ideas For 2023"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Calling all people who have a thing for home bars! Create a space to host your wine tastings and to shake up those mocktails.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Homes are becoming a hub for so many activities these days. Working, working out and partying! Homeowners today have lifestyle aspirations and consciously like to bring in lots of comfort and conveniences to their homes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, aside from regular rooms, balconies, patios, and decor, home bars are an excellent add-on to a well-designed home. Get one and sit back in your comfortable pyjamas, pour your favourite glass of Bourbon as we present you the hottest (<em>and coolest<\/em>) home bar design ideas of 2023 for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Whiskey On The Rocks, Rustic Style Home Bar Design!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Home bars come in a plethora of styles and nothing allures us more than this rustic style bar. Bring in the old cowboy style salons into your living space with distressed wood, stone, bricks, and sturdy stools built for men who can handle their liquor. Hang up a chalkboard with the days\u2019 drink (for a bar like a feel). Do not include coasters and cocktail napkins because a few spills and tarnishes blend in perfectly well with a rustic style bar (<em>pun unintended<\/em>)! The Old-West may be decades behind us but the revival of the rustic theme will probably make your bar a legend of its own.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012152\/rustic-style-home-bar-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Home bar design in rustic style bring in the old cowboy style is a one of the best home bar idea in 2023\" class=\"wp-image-6597\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012152\/rustic-style-home-bar-designs.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012152\/rustic-style-home-bar-designs-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012152\/rustic-style-home-bar-designs-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012152\/rustic-style-home-bar-designs-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A rustic theme bar will ooze out the good, bad, and the ugly.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"941\" height=\"2083\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/15143112\/storage-ideas-for-home-bar.jpg\" alt=\"Home bars with storage ideas\" class=\"wp-image-52373\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/15143112\/storage-ideas-for-home-bar.jpg 941w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/15143112\/storage-ideas-for-home-bar-136x300.jpg 136w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/15143112\/storage-ideas-for-home-bar-463x1024.jpg 463w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/15143112\/storage-ideas-for-home-bar-768x1700.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/15143112\/storage-ideas-for-home-bar-694x1536.jpg 694w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/15143112\/storage-ideas-for-home-bar-925x2048.jpg 925w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/15143112\/storage-ideas-for-home-bar-150x332.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 941px) 100vw, 941px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Monk Hides Behind The <em>Old <\/em>Closet<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you house a cabinet you don&#8217;t use anymore? Ever thought of turning it into a tavern right at home? A storage bar will work wonders despite its size. A simple unused cabinet can be transformed into a minibar with working sinks and ample space to store your expensive liquor and glasses. Hosting parties will become much easier if you have a dedicated mixing station rather than looking for a corner counter. The coolest thing about having a cabinet bar is that you can hide your bottles from your children after the party is over.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012156\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-cabinets.jpg\" alt=\"Home mini bar designs with a simple unused cabinet and home bar unit\" class=\"wp-image-6598\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012156\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-cabinets.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012156\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-cabinets-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012156\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-cabinets-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012156\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-cabinets-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Make a closet a fully functioning minibar and see the intoxicating effect it has<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Related Articles:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-horizontal is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-1 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/modern-home-bar-designs\/\">Modern Home Bar Designs<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/hidden-bar-cabinet-ideas\/\">Hidden Bar Cabinets<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-bar-stools\/\">Kitchen Bar Stools<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Flaunt Your Antiquity: A Home Bar Design With Mirrors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bring in the effortless style of a pub into your living room by adding personalised bar mirrors. If you are an ardent collector of expensive spirits, adding mirrors will make your cabinets appear bigger plus you get to flaunt your prized collections. Mirrors bring out the beauty of glassware and bottles, add depth and reflect light.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012159\/home-bar-designs-with-mirrors-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Home bar designs by adding personalised bar mirrors gives modern look home bar design\" class=\"wp-image-6599\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012159\/home-bar-designs-with-mirrors-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012159\/home-bar-designs-with-mirrors-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012159\/home-bar-designs-with-mirrors-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012159\/home-bar-designs-with-mirrors-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Mirror mirror on the wall, which is the most expensive liquor of them all?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Get Your Home Ready For Fun &amp; Safe House Parties | Home Bar Designs | Dining Room Designs\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/bLCm1LoBdCE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Your Magic Moments Are Safe With a Corner Home Bar<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We have explored various ways on how to utilise empty corners in your home. So the addition of a snazzy mini bar is a great idea. Most homes have an underutilised corner at an odd angle. A small mini bar is a perfect fit for this little niche and a great way to save space. Floating shelves, mounted cabinets, a stand for all those wine glasses, and a stylish rack with cool lighting complete the look of a corner bar.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012203\/corner-home-mini-bar-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Corner bar designs great way to save space with mini bar unit\" class=\"wp-image-6600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012203\/corner-home-mini-bar-designs.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012203\/corner-home-mini-bar-designs-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012203\/corner-home-mini-bar-designs-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012203\/corner-home-mini-bar-designs-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Who says corner minibars are outdated? Check this out<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make It Absolut-ly Charming With Wallpapers And Murals!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Set the perfect mood for your guests and let the good times rock! Build it along with your living room area so you can relax as you enjoy an evening drink. Walking into a mini bar like this will rejuvenate your body after a stressful day. A fabulous wallpaper will do wonders! Now you can enjoy a lovely glass of wine to begin your evening or use your bar as a space to enjoy the weekend with your buddies.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012207\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-wallpapers.jpg\" alt=\"Home mini bar designs with a fabulous wallpapers makes home bar designs beautiful\" class=\"wp-image-6601\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012207\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-wallpapers.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012207\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-wallpapers-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012207\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-wallpapers-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012207\/home-mini-bar-designs-with-wallpapers-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you like the idea of how you can design a bar in your home. Feel free to add in some ideas and designs if we missed out any. If you have some awesome home bar ideas you think we can feature here, please mention them in the comments section below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Explore, More About<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a hr